Class CargoAircraftTechData

  • java.lang.Object
    • by.zyablov.airlinecompany.beans.techdata.CargoAircraftTechData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UniqueAircraftTechDataBehavior, java.io.Serializable

    public class CargoAircraftTechData
extends java.lang.Object
implements UniqueAircraftTechDataBehavior, java.io.Serializable
    Class CargoAircraftTechData represents a unique technical information for CargoAircraft class such as a size of cargo depatment size of a cargo aircraft in cubic meters and opportunity to transport danger goods on board of a cargo aircraft.

    Class CargoAircraftTechData implements UniqueAircraftTechDataBehavior to show that's CargoAircraft can have such unique technical information.
